                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "The current status of the agreement. Typical values are: in process, approved and rejected.  \n* `initialized` Initialized  \n* `inProcess` In process  \n* `validated` Validated  \n* `pendingUpdate` Pending update  \n* `rejected` Rejected  ",
